Cost Accounting
	One SVP entry:
		tag: 20 bits
		conf: 2 bits
		retired_value: 64 bits
		stride: 64 bits
		instance ctr: 9 bits
		bits/SVP entry: 159 bits
	Total storage cost (bits) = 1024 (159 SVP entries x 162816 bits/SVP entry) = 162816 bits
